name: JournArt
description: JournArt is a crypto project that introduces a unique collection of JournArt DogGirls NFTs designed to evoke significant emotions, excitement, and satisfaction. These NFTs are exquisitely valuable, and users can acquire them by purchasing $JART tokens, which are the native tokens built on the Binance Smartchain. The $JART token comes with a unique Reflection feature that rewards holders with 10% of every sell transaction made across the entire JournArt ecosystem. The project plans to release a brilliant collection of NFTs that will add beauty and value to the world of NFTs while improving the existing standards. In addition, JournArt plans to launch a decentralized exchange (DEX) that will provide users with a more satisfying trading experience. The JournArt DEX will be fast, secure, and user-friendly, ensuring that users can trade their $JART tokens and NFTs with ease. With its adorable JournArt DogGirls NFTs, $JART tokens, Reflection feature, and plans for a DEX, JournArt is well-positioned to become a leading player in the crypto space.
